import React from 'react';
import {Container, Row, Col} from "react-bootstrap";

const roundblock = {
    borderRadius: '500px',
    borderColor: 'black',
    width: '400px',
    height: '300px',
    backgroundColor: '#black',
    display: 'block',
    marginTop: '200px',
    marginLeft: 'auto',
    marginRight: 'auto',
    //How to center the button ???
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: 'center'
}


export const Home = (props) => (
    <>
        <Container>
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center" style={roundblock} >
                <Col md="auto">Variable width content</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col md="auto">Second Column</Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>

    </>


)
